<p>Dream home plans: The former TOWIE star, 30, and her spouse, 35, purchased a run down 1920s property earlier this year and had dreamed of turning it into a five-bedroom £1.4 million dream home over a planned year and a half long project</p>

<p>Earlier this month, Billie shared a picture of toasting a glass of wine with Greg to their home Instagram account called 'homewiththesheps'. </p>

<p>She wrote: 'We are so excited that we can FINALLY announce that our Planning Permission has been APPROVED ✔️❤️ </p>

<p> 'I know we have been extremely quiet on here due to waiting for the permission, but we can now look forward to sharing lots of updates with you all on our huge renovation project ❤️.'</p>

<p>The Mummy Diaries continues at 9pm on ITVBe. </p>

